Photocarrefour, an independent photogallery in Abuja, is finally opening its postponed exhibition entitled Movement. The exhibition opens several months after its postponement in 2021 following the onset of the COVID-19 pandemic and the subsequent global lockdowns. Movement will feature the photographic works of a diverse group of photographers as they explore the concept of movement. Exhibition opens March 26 till April 10, 2022 at the photocarrefour gallery, at the Mabushi, Ultra Modern Market, Jahi, Abuja. 